				\begin{document}$$ {E}_{\left(\lambda, T\right)}=\frac{2\pi h{c}^2}{\lambda^5\left( \exp \left(\frac{hc}{\lambda KT}\right)-1\right)}, $$\end{document}where h is the Planck’s constant, K the Boltzmann constant and c the speed of the light in the vacuum.

